                            h2 Pop-up Warnings
                            p A Pop-Up warning is a window or message that suddenly appears on your device’s screen, claiming that your device has been infected or has a security issue and you need to call the indicated number to fix it. The message may look like it is coming from your antivirus software or your operating system (e.g., Microsoft Windows, macOS) by using their logos and other branding information. [3]

