                            h2 Online ads
                            p Scammers try to reach their victims by making their FAKE “tech support” websites appear in internet search results. They pay for online advertisements to promote their fake services. Search engines, like Google, place ads before the list of search results, making it more likely that people will click the ad. If you are searching for reputable tech support companies, be sure you scroll past the ads.


